Note:
    > to check the docker image created, run below command on EC2 terminal
        > sudo docker ps
    > to check logs in container, run below command
        > sudo docker logs <container-id>
    > to stop a container, run below command
        > docker stop <container-id>
    > to remove an image / container, run below command
        > docker rm <container-id>

